Symphony of the Night</i>, or <i>Guacamelee!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/3620bc3ec0bb59b602f5ea012ce745e4.poster.avif?t=1773334142\" width=612 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/3620bc3ec0bb59b602f5ea012ce745e4.webm?t=1773334142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/3620bc3ec0bb59b602f5ea012ce745e4.mp4?t=1773334142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Key Features:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the Martian colony:</strong> discover new biomes, secrets, and numerous threats along the way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face your enemies:</strong> perform combos by mixing melee and ranged attacks, as well as special moves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use different equipment and abilities:</strong> find upgrades and new skills while exploring the Martian colony.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engage in epic battles:</strong> from deadly robots to colossal monsters, build your strategies, uncover their weaknesses, and survive!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play it your way:</strong> with various accessibility options, you can customize the game according to your style and needs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/951c28275ec0abeaffa3a08122bf08d2.poster.avif?t=1773334142\" width=616 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/951c28275ec0abeaffa3a08122bf08d2.webm?t=1773334142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/951c28275ec0abeaffa3a08122bf08d2.mp4?t=1773334142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
